title: Farberware FMO11AHTBKBD1 Countertop 1000 Watts Microwave Oven with LED Lighting and Child Lock-Perfect for Apartments and Dorms-Easy Clean, 1.1 Cu. Ft, Stainless Steel
description: This microwave oven is the ideal size for office break rooms or home kitchens. One-touch cooking programs let you cook six of the most popular food items with the touch of a button. Choose from ten power levels up to 1000. The large digital screen has a clock feature and can display a countdown timer in addition to the remaining cook time. The memory function lets you customize and save your favorite settings, and the large door has an easy-grip handle and child-safety lock.
